      • getTickData

        java.util.List<Tick> getTickData(Instrument instrument,
                                 long time,
                                 int oneSecondIntervalsBefore,
                                 int oneSecondIntervalsAfter)
                          throws ServerException
        Returns ticks for the instrument.
        Parameters:
        instrument - The instrument.
        time - Time of the last one second tick interval in period specified in oneSecondIntervalsBefore parameter or/and time of the one second tick interval prior first one second tick interval in period specified with oneSecondIntervalsAfter parameter.
        oneSecondIntervalsBefore - Number of one second ticks intervals to include before and including the time parameter.
        oneSecondIntervalsAfter - Number of one second ticks intervals to include after, not including the time parameter.
        Returns:
        The list of ticks.
        Throws:
        ServerException - If a server error occurs.

        periodsAfter - Number of periods after not including the period starting at the reference time.

        The list of price data items.
